TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Pre SQL
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: UPDATE IN_ETL_CONTROL A SET TXT_KEY_VALUE=(SELECT LPAD(TO_CHAR(NVL(TO_NUMBER(A.TXT_KEY_VALUE),0)+TO_NUMBER(B.TXT_KEY_VALUE)),10,'0') FROM IN_ETL_CONTROL B WHERE TXT_KEY_STRING='POSITION_ELIGIBLE_RECORD_COUNT' and DEC_RUNNING_FLG=1), DTE_UPDATE_DATE=SYSDATE WHERE TXT_KEY_STRING='POSITION_STAGE_RECORD_COUNT' and DEC_RUNNING_FLG=1; COMMIT;
